@startuml ActivityDiagram
|Student|
start
:Login to LearnMesh;
:Update Profile Information;
:Set Learning Preferences;
note right
  - Skill Level
  - Availability
  - Learning Style
  - Subject Interests
end note

|System|
:Collect User Data;
:Analyze User Profile;

if (Existing Groups Available?) then (yes)
  :Run Matching Algorithm;
  :Calculate Compatibility Scores;
  
  if (Good Match Found?) then (yes)
    :Send Group Recommendation;
    
    |Student|
    if (Accept Recommendation?) then (yes)
      |System|
      :Add User to Group;
      :Send Real-time Notification via WebSocket;
      
      |Student|
      :Join Group Session;
      :Collaborate with Peers;
      :Provide Feedback;
      
      |System|
      :Update User Statistics;
      :Adjust Matching Parameters;
    else (no)
      :Request New Match;
      |System|
      :Re-run Algorithm;
    endif
  else (no)
    |System|
    :Create New Group;
    :Add User as First Member;
    :Wait for More Members;
  endif
else (no)
  :Create New Group;
  :Set User as Group Creator;
endif

stop
@enduml
